---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
const buildDate = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 10);
---

<footer class="border-t border-ink mt-24 bg-paper">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-5">
        <p class="font-display italic text-3xl leading-none text-ink mb-3">Worth a letter?</p>
        <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm max-w-md">
          Open to applied AI, quant, DS, and forward-deployed roles. Paris first, London close second. Or just to say hello.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:jevan.cousins@gmail.com"
          class="ink-link mono text-[0.78rem] tracking-widest uppercase mt-4 inline-block"
        >
          jevan.cousins@gmail.com →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-3">
        <p class="label mb-3">Elsewhere</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mono text-[0.78rem] uppercase tracking-widest">
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/jevancousins" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="nav-link text-ink hover:text-oxide">
              GitHub ↗
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/jevancousins" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="nav-link text-ink hover:text-oxide">
              LinkedIn ↗
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/now" class="nav-link text-ink hover:text-oxide">
              What I'm doing now →
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="col-span-6 md:col-span-4">
        <p class="label mb-3">Colophon</p>
        <p class="mono text-[0.72rem] text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
          Set in <span class="text-ink">Instrument Serif</span>, <span class="text-ink">Newsreader</span>, and <span class="text-ink">JetBrains Mono</span>. Built with Astro and Tailwind. Hand-drafted in London.
        </p>
        <p class="mono text-[0.7rem] text-ink-faint mt-3">
          Edition {currentYear} · Build {buildDate}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="rule mt-10 mb-4" />
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mono text-[0.68rem] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-faint">
      <span>© {currentYear} Jevan Cousins</span>
      <span>Folio · END</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
